OL,3,CBlack bins to be collected once every
OL,4,Cthree weeks to save #1m
OL,6,FResidents in South Gloucestershire
OL,7,Fwill have their black bins collected
OL,8,Fonce every three weeks from 2026 to
OL,9,Fsave just over #1 million a year.
OL,11,FThe new regime, created to cut costs
OL,12,Fand encourage people to recycle more,
OL,13,Fis expected to be formally signed off
OL,14,Fdespite concerns of bins overflowing.
OL,16,FResidents in the district currently
OL,17,Fget their black bins collected every
OL,18,Ftwo weeks.
OL,20,FFees to have garden waste collected
OL,21,Fhave also doubled from #30 to #60.
