OL,6,FSouth Gloucestershire Council bosses
OL,7,Fare expected to approve the changes
OL,8,Fduring a cabinet meeting on Monday 11
OL,9,FNovember.
OL,11,FThe changes form part of a wider new
OL,12,Fcontract with Suez, for collecting
OL,13,Fbins over the next eight years.
