OL,6,FA cabinet report said: "There have
OL,7,Fbeen numerous consultation and
OL,8,Fengagement events and exercises to
OL,9,Fensure residents and stakeholders are
OL,10,Ffully briefed, informed and involved
OL,11,Fwhere possible in the decision-making
OL,12,Fprocess. These proposed service
OL,13,Fchanges will provide savings to ensure
OL,14,Fthe council continues to provide a
OL,15,Fviable ongoing waste service offer to
OL,16,Fresidents.
